{"tid":2406692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★黑天鵝作者：比特幣是一場「失敗」，一種貨幣不應較買來的東西價格更波動","createTime":"2021-02-13T12:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T04:58:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"67f9795f2bd4a8a6236255701060ded5a376d7eb","tid":2406692,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"虛擬貨幣「一哥」比特幣近日破頂之際，其爭議依然不斷！因《黑天鵝效應》(The Black Swan)一書而在經濟學及投資界打響名堂的塔利布(Nassim Nicholas Taleb)稱已把持有的比特幣脫手。<br />\n<br />\n塔利布周五(12)在Twitter推文中解釋，一種貨幣不應該較買來的東西價格更加波動，直言比特幣不能為商品定價，是一場「失敗(至少到目前為止)」。他在另一則推文中稱，比特幣無法作為對沖央行政策的避險工具。<br />\n而一直唱淡虛擬貨幣、被稱為「末日博士」的著名經濟學家魯比尼日前再批評比特幣的基本價值為零，若要對因「挖礦」而產生的污染徵稅，其價值更加淪為負值，並警告比特幣泡沫會再次爆破。他又重申，比特幣並非計價單位及可以合理比較規模的支付工具，更不是穩定的儲值工具，將加密貨幣視作資產屬誤導<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210213/bkn-20210213191707507-0213_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210213%2Fbkn-20210213191707507-0213_00842_001.html&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=8955cfc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210213/bkn-20210213191707507-0213_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"67de98835bc1a972afe08198fcc69d3864fe3cd1","tid":2406692,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e08b3fc24b97101f14dc3016a61b4fceec30a9","tid":2406692,"uid":250055,"like":7,"dislike":25,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"因為bitcoin要時間發展<br />\n<br />